entries.femaleVariant: Hey choom, I uh... think the building's sinking, y'know? When I put that level on it, I--
Shut up! Fuck's sake, you wanna get fired?
I know it's sinkin', everyone knows it's sinkin' – except the investor. Word gets out – bam, no more building. And we are out of a job.
You wanna be out on your ass? No? Then shut up and do your job.
